text: Update: got one of the CV based localization systems working with the Boston set, (these are <@U4K0WAADP> s linked ones) - it only saves when it's certain (only about 10% of the time) so I'm going to modify it to save ones it's unsure of and then pipe everything through the CNN that's currently ~84%
The plan after that is to use this to hand craft a newer more concise training set
The localizer does a good job of getting in the areas of interest
It's just a little too hard on itself. Currently walking over to GoPro some runners
This black on blue for the 15k is gonna be rough, but interesting
